title: Meet Me in Melbourne March 30, 31, Apr 1 2019
description:
March 30 2019 Conference https://petersonphenomenon.org/

For tickets https://www.eventbrite.com.au/d/australia--docklands/the-jordan-peterson-phenomenon/

Saturday 30th conference at St James Old Cathedral, cnr King and Batman sts West Melbourne, 9:00am -6:00pm approx. Lunch provided.

Dinner in a restaurant in Carlton by invitation at 7:00pm to team and supporters.

 Sunday 31st Free until evangelistic meeting 7:00-8:00pm at St James Conference Centre. Dinner before.

 Monday 1st April Free for sightseeing.

Meet up in the St James Old Cathedral Conference Center, 6-8.00pm. Coffee, tea and biscuits (cookies) only. Dinner afterward.
